creator: Westfield Union Manhattan Bagel
descriptionHtml:
The Westfield Union Manhattan Bagel app is a convenient way to pay in store or skip the line and order ahead. Rewards are built right in, so you'll collect Stars and start earning free drinks and food with every purchase.
Pay in store
Save time and earn Rewards when you pay with the Westfield Union Manhattan Bagel app at our stores.
Order ahead
Customize and place your order, and pick up from a nearby store without waiting in line.
Rewards
Track your Stars and redeem Rewards for a free food or drink of your choosing. Receive custom offers as a Manhattan Bagel Rewards™ member.
